---
import FadeIn from "./fade-in";
---

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="from-brand-green to-brand-blue absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 h-56 w-screen -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-linear-to-r lg:h-60"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative grid items-center gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div class="relative z-10 py-12 lg:py-18">
        <FadeIn
          client:visible
          as="h2"
          className="text-center text-(length:--step-5)/20 font-bold tracking-[0.125em] text-white uppercase"
        >
          Feel Better
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
      <FadeIn
        client:visible
        disableBlur
        className="relative z-10 col-start-2 flex w-full items-center justify-center"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/herbert.webp"
          alt="Dr. Herbert Maradiaga"
          class="aspect-4/3 h-96 border-6 border-white object-cover object-center"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </FadeIn>

      <div class="relative z-10 py-12 lg:py-18">
        <FadeIn
          client:visible
          as="h2"
          className="text-center text-(length:--step-5)/20 font-bold tracking-[0.125em] text-white uppercase"
        >
          THAN EVER
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <FadeIn
    client:visible
    as="div"
    className="mx-auto mt-10 grid max-w-5xl justify-center gap-8 px-4 pt-10 text-(length:--step-0)/8 text-neutral-900 lg:mt-6 lg:grid-cols-1 lg:gap-8 lg:px-24"
    delay={0.1}
  >
    <p class="">
      Desde 2010 somos expertos en metabolismo, equilibrio hormonal y bienestar
      integral. Hemos construido clínicas especializadas donde la experiencia
      médica y la tecnología avanzada trabajan para una sola meta:
      <span
        class="mt-8 block text-(length:--step-0)/8 font-semibold text-neutral-950"
      >
        Que te sientas mejor que nunca.
      </span>
    </p>

    <p>
      Por eso nuestro lema es Feel Better Than Ever. <br />No es solo un slogan.
      <br />
      Es una promesa.
    </p>
    <img
      src="https://onlinepngtools.com/images/examples-onlinepngtools/george-walker-bush-signature.png"
      alt=""
      class="h-16 place-self-end"
    />
  </FadeIn>
</section>
